      "title": "Bail for Hirunika and others",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "(5.12 PM) The 11 people arrested including Mrs. Hirunika Premachandra have been released on police bail.",
        "The police said that nine people were arrested, including Mrs. Hirunika Premachandra, former Member of Parliament.",
        "The group was arrested while protesting near the entrance gate of the Fort President's House."
